        <content>
          <p>SECTION 3.  PRESERVATION AND MANAGEMENT
OF SUCCESSION PROPERTY
Art. 3221.  Preservation of succession property
A succession representative shall preserve, repair, maintain, and protect the property of the succession.</p>
